    - candidate: look-for-pattern-not-counterexample
        - location: lines 2029-2098 (section "Look for Patterns" plus the same-behavior-different-interpretation table). The table pairs (shy/aloof, upbeat/phony, spontaneous/flaky, truth-teller/nasty, passionate/emotional, smart/arrogant, high-standards/hypercritical, outgoing/overbearing, quirky/annoying) is the chapter's diagnostic instrument.
